{"article_id":"egOONa72dSgDXhsO","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"PHOENIX ( ) -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump revved up supporters on Tuesday with a defense of his response to a white supremacist-organized rally in Virginia and a promise","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to shut down the U.S. government","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"if necessary","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"to build a wall along the border with Mexico .","depth":6},{"id":5,"text":"U.S. President Donald Trump speaks at a campaign rally in Phoenix , Arizona , U.S. , August 22 , 2017 .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"/Joshua Roberts","depth":5},{"id":7,"text":"Under fire","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"for saying","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"\" both sides \" were to blame for the violence between white supremacists and left-wing counter protesters in Virginia on Aug. 12 ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"Trump accused television networks of ignoring his calls for unity in the aftermath .","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"\" I didn ' t say","depth":10},{"id":12,"text":"I love you","depth":12},{"id":13,"text":"because you ' re black ,","depth":12},{"id":14,"text":"or I love you","depth":12},{"id":15,"text":"because you ' re white , \"","depth":12},{"id":16,"text":"Trump said .","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"\" I love all the people of our country . \"","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"Police used pepper spray","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"to disperse crowds","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"after protesters threw rocks and bottles outside the convention center","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"where Trump spoke ,","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"police said .","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"Trump ,","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"who often uses news organizations as a foil ,","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"repeatedly singled out the media for criticism","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"of how it covered the violence in the Virginia college town of Charlottesville and the resulting political fallout .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" These are truly dishonest people .","depth":11},{"id":28,"text":"They ' re bad people .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"I really think","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"they don ' t like our country , \"","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"\" The only people","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"giving a platform to these hate groups","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"is the media . \"","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"Adopting a glib tone ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"Trump said","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"many reporters ignored his condemnation of white supremacists , including the Ku Klux Klan .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"\" I hit ' em with neo-Nazi ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"I hit ' em with everything ...","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"KKK ?","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"We have KKK .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"I got ' em all , \"","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"James Clapper , a former director of U.S. national intelligence , expressed concern at Trump ' s performance ,","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"calling it \" downright scary and disturbing . \"","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"\" I question his fitness","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"to be in office , \"","depth":9},{"id":48,"text":"Clapper told CNN .","depth":8},{"id":49,"text":"Funding for the border wall has flagged in the U.S. Congress","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"as many lawmakers question","depth":10},{"id":51,"text":"whether Trump ' s main promise during the 2016 presidential election campaign is really necessary .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"But","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"with a budget battle looming ,","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"Trump said","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"he would be willing to risk a politically damaging government shutdown","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"in order to secure funding for the wall .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"He visited the border region in Yuma , Arizona , earlier on Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"\" If we have to close down our government ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"we ' re building that wall , \"","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"Trump said .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"\" We ' re going to have our wall .","depth":10},{"id":62,"text":"The American people voted for immigration control .","depth":10},{"id":63,"text":"We ' re going to get that wall . \"","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"With thousands of supporters cheering him on ,","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"Trump also weighed in on another racially charged issue ,","depth":8},{"id":66,"text":"hinting","depth":9},{"id":67,"text":"he would pardon former Maricopa County Sheriff Joe Arpaio .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Arpaio , 85 ,","depth":12},{"id":69,"text":"who battled illegal immigration in the Phoenix area ,","depth":12},{"id":70,"text":"was found guilty last month of criminal contempt","depth":12},{"id":71,"text":"for violating the terms of a 2011 court order in a racial profiling case .","depth":12},{"id":72,"text":"Trump covered the gamut of issues , from NAFTA trade talks to the U.S. showdown with North Korea , during a raucous , rambling and defiant political speech","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"lasting an hour and 15 minutes .","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"He said","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"he might terminate the NAFTA treaty with Mexico and Canada","depth":12},{"id":76,"text":"to jumpstart negotiations ,","depth":12},{"id":77,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"the standoff with North Korea over its weapons programs might have taken a positive turn .","depth":11},{"id":79,"text":"However , it was unclear whether the speech would help lay the foundation for a comeback from the deep political crisis","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"Trump finds himself in after only seven months in office and an approval rating below 40 percent .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"He expressed frustration","depth":12},{"id":82,"text":"that the Republican-controlled Congress was unable to approve healthcare legislation","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"that failed to pass the Senate by one vote last month .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"One of the votes against the legislation was cast by Republican Senator John McCain of Arizona ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"who was recently diagnosed with brain cancer .","depth":12},{"id":86,"text":"Without mentioning their names ,","depth":11},{"id":87,"text":"Trump criticized both McCain and his fellow Arizona Republican , Senator Jeff Flake .","depth":11},{"id":88,"text":"Trump complained repeatedly about the \" one vote \"","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"that stopped the Senate from repealing and replacing Obamacare , the signature domestic policy of his predecessor , Barack Obama .","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"\" One vote away .","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"I will not mention any names","depth":13},{"id":92,"text":"- very presidential .","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"And nobody wants me to mention your other senator ,","depth":14},{"id":94,"text":"who ' s weak on border , weak on crime .","depth":15},{"id":95,"text":"Nobody knows","depth":16},{"id":96,"text":"who the hell he is !","depth":16},{"id":97,"text":"See ,","depth":15},{"id":98,"text":"I haven ' t mentioned any names ,","depth":15},{"id":99,"text":"so now everybody ' s happy , \"","depth":14},{"id":100,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":101,"text":"The White House had said earlier","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"when asked about Arpaio","depth":11},{"id":103,"text":"that \" there will be no discussion of that today . \"","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"\" Do the people in this room like Sheriff Joe ? \"","depth":12},{"id":105,"text":"Trump asked ,","depth":12},{"id":106,"text":"sparking loud applause and a chant of \" Pardon Joe ! \"","depth":11},{"id":107,"text":"\" Was Sheriff Joe convicted","depth":14},{"id":108,"text":"for doing his job ? \"","depth":14},{"id":109,"text":"Trump asked ,","depth":13},{"id":110,"text":"before predicting","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"that Arpaio would be just fine .","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"\" I won ' t do it tonight","depth":14},{"id":113,"text":"because I don ' t want to cause any controversy .","depth":14},{"id":114,"text":"But Sheriff Joe can feel good , \"","depth":13},{"id":115,"text":"he said .","depth":12},{"id":116,"text":"Trump drew broad criticism","depth":8},{"id":117,"text":"for blaming both white nationalists and counter-protesters for the deadly violence at the Charlottesville rally ,","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"which was organized by neo-Nazis and white supremacists .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"One woman was killed .","depth":9},{"id":120,"text":"Protesters outside Tuesday ' s rally yelled :","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"\" Shame , shame , shame \"","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"and \" No Trump , No KKK , No fascist USA \"","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"as the Trump supporters began filing into the Phoenix Convention Center .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"Supporters ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"who lined up for hours in the Arizona heat ahead of the event ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"chanted :","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"\" Build the wall. \"","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"Many wore red hats with Trump ' s campaign slogan , \" Make America Great Again . \"","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"Trump has held a series of 2020 re-election campaign stops","depth":5},{"id":130,"text":"despite only having taken office in January .","depth":5},{"id":131,"text":"Phoenix Mayor Greg Stanton , a Democrat , had asked him to postpone Tuesday ' s event","depth":5},{"id":132,"text":"while the nation healed from outrage and division after the deadly rally in Charlottesville .","depth":5},{"id":133,"text":"A heavy police presence was deployed around the Phoenix venue for Trump ' s first trip as president to Arizona ,","depth":4},{"id":134,"text":"which he won in the 2016 election .","depth":4}],"relations":[{"parent":269,"left":0,"right":268,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":2